'''Sharoobo'''
[[File:12-08-18-tilidin-retard.jpg|thumb|Noocyo kala duwan oo daawada ka mid ah.]]

'''Sharoobo''' ([[Ingiriis]]: Syrup) waa [[dareere]] kimiko ka samaysan [[isku dhis]]yo dhowr nooc ah, taas oo loogu talo galay ineey la dagaalanto [[xanuun]]. 

[[Dawo|Dawada]] sharoobooyinka waxa laga qaataa [[af]]ka kaas oo [[calool|caloosha]] taga ka dib markuu milmo raaca [[xidid]]ada [[dhiig]]a, qaar kale maqaarka sare ee [[jidh]]ka ayaa la mariyaa. 

Guud ahaan, dawadu waxay u kala baxdaa labo nooc: mid [[dareere]] ah, sida [[sharoobo]]oyinka; iyo mid [[adke]] yaryar ah sida kiniinka. 

Intaas waxaa dheer, daawada waxa laga sameeyaa [[dhir]]ta, [[macdan]]ta, [[xoolo|xoolaha]], kimikooyin la isku darey iyo xataa waxyaabo laga keeno [[bad]]aha. 

